		{
			"name": "Slot Tools",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Get Available Slots - Today",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"method\": \"tools/call\",\n    \"params\": {\n        \"name\": \"get_available_slots\",\n        \"arguments\": {\n            \"practitioner_id\": \"practitioner-003\",\n            \"date_option\": \"today\"\n        }\n    }\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/mcp",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["mcp"]
						},
						"description": "Get available slots for Dr. Lee (Dermatology) for today.\n\n**Arguments:**\n- `practitioner_id` (string): Practitioner ID from list_practitioners_by_specialty\n- `date_option` (string): One of: \"today\", \"tomorrow\", or YYYY-MM-DD format\n\n**Returns:**\n- `available_slots` (array): List with `slot_id`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `display`\n- `slot_count` (number): Number of available slots"
					}
				},
